sentences: Robert Jack Duarte Wallace (born April 7, 1986 in Mexico City, Distrito Federal) is a Mexican actor and singer.
During his time in the boy band M5,  Duarte toured through various countries in Latin America including Bolivia, Peru, Ecuador, El Salvador, Costa Rica, Guatemala, and Honduras.
Duarte was a member of the musical group, Eme 15 from 2011 until the group's separation in December 2014.
